column5: The Maina Vent 3! This short vent includes one from Pete's son Seth, the "Mini-Maina"! This vent also includes a 5 minute song performed by Brian Schram "Fishless Blues"...catch it on Rockin' Fish Tales 2!   http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NdjiW4oMNkc
Good stuff Pete, Seth. Thanks Nate. Ok OK and the Schram band isn't bad either.
Seth is pretty good at this vent thing... He will have his own show soon
